@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_repltn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.45
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.28) - v0)
    v1 = v1
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.cos(tmp + 0.92) + (v0 + 0.47 - v1 + 0.45)))
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.exp(v2 + 0.62) * (v1 + 0.14 + v2 + 0.08)))
    v2 = wp.abs(0.84)
    v2 = (v1 / ((tmp + 0.25 + v2 + 0.49) - wp.cos(v2 + 0.48)))
    v2 = 0.52
    data[tid] = v0
